{"word":"Josiah","slug":"josiah","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Josiah</b> <a href=\"#/H2977\">H2977</a> <br/> 1. King of Judah:<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=21&verse=26'>2Ki 21:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=22&verse=1'>2Ki 22:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=3&verse=14'>1Ch 3:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=33&verse=25'>2Ch 33:25</a> <br/> - Ancestor of Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=1&verse=11'>Mat 1:11</a> <br/> - Slain in battle with Pharaoh Nechoh<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=23&verse=30'>2Ki 23:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=35&verse=24'>2Ch 35:24</a> <br/> - Lamentations for<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=35&verse=25'>2Ch 35:25</a> <br/> - Piety of, exemplified in his repairing the temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=22&verse=7'>2Ki 22:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=34&verse=4'>2Ch 34:4</a> <br/> - Solicitude when the copy of the law was discovered and read to him<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=22&verse=20'>2Ki 22:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=34&verse=33'>2Ch 34:33</a> <br/> - Solicitude in keeping a solemn Passover<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=23&verse=23'>2Ki 23:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=35&verse=19'>2Ch 35:19</a> <br/> - Called Josias<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=1&verse=11'>Mat 1:11</a> <br/> - Prophecies concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=13&verse=3'>1Ki 13:3</a> <br/> - Destroys the altar and high places of idolatry<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=23&verse=20'>2Ki 23:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=23&verse=25'>2Ki 23:25</a> <br/> 2. Son of Zephaniah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=6&verse=10'>Zec 6:10</a>"}]}